reviewText: I enjoy with my grandson the further tales of Max and Ruby the bunnies. This is one of Ethan's favorites.
Title: Max and Ruby: Berry Bunny Adventures

reviewText: Always love Ruby and Max, but love Max best.  Nice calm show and Max and his attitude just crack me up.  You can practically hear him humph when Ruby tells him to do something that he does not care to do.
Title: Max and Ruby: Berry Bunny Adventures

reviewText: Our son loves Max and Ruby. The program is a great teaching tool of how to ask for things and talk to people without being rude.
Title: Max and Ruby: Berry Bunny Adventures

reviewText: Very good stories and very entertaining for my toddler.She can sit and watch for hours and actively engages with the stories.Very Clean and watchable unlike some of the Goofy tv shows like Sponge Bob that makes you feel like your a crackhead for watching.
Title: Max and Ruby: Berry Bunny Adventures
